# AI Interaction Guidelines

## Code Changes
- Only implement when confidence is high
- Check for existing solutions
- Follow project patterns
- Document decisions
- Implement incrementally

## Problem Solving
- Understand the problem
- Research solutions
- Evaluate trade-offs
- Document findings
- Implement best solution

## Communication
- Be clear and specific
- Keep the explanations short and bulleted
- Explain the changes in 1-2 lines
- Provide context
- Explain technical concepts
- Ask for clarification
- Document decisions


